import * as React from "react";
import {
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  FormErrorMessage,
  FormHelperText,
  Input,
  Button,
  Container,
  Flex,
  Box,
  Image,
  HStack,
  InputGroup,
  Select,
  Textarea,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import * as yup from "yup";
import { useForm } from "react-hook-form";
import { yupResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/yup";

const schema = yup.object().shape({
  name: yup.string().required(),
  email: yup.string().email().required(),
  subject: yup.string().required(),
  enquiry: yup.string().required(),
  textarea: yup.string().required()
});

type LoginFormInputs = {
  name: string;
  email: string;
  subject: string;
  enquiry: string;
  textarea: string;
};

export default function Contact() {
  const { register, handleSubmit, errors } = useForm({
    mode: "onBlur",
    resolver: yupResolver(schema)
  });

  return (
    <Container maxW={1124} mx="auto">
      <Flex>
        <Box mt="70px" mr="40px" height="190px">
          <Image
            bg="#e6ffff"
            src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/foodieland-3b1ed.appspot.com/o/cooker%2FCook-contact.png?alt=media&token=6d41b736-1b6c-4929-9b2e-fd6319ebfa2b"
          />
        </Box>
        <Box mt="40px" w="100%">
          <form style={{ width: 350 }}>
            <HStack spacing="50px" mb="15px">
              <FormControl
                isInvalid={!!errors?.name?.message}
                errortext={errors?.name?.message}
                p="4"
                isRequired
              >
                <FormLabel>Name</FormLabel>
                <Input
                  type="text"
                  name="name"
                  placeholder="Name"
                  ref={register}
                />
                <FormErrorMessage>{errors?.name?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
                <FormHelperText>
                  We are obviously giving this straight to Facebook.
                </FormHelperText>
              </FormControl>
              <FormControl
                isInvalid={!!errors?.email?.message}
                errortext={errors?.email?.message}
                p="4"
                isRequired
              >
                <FormLabel>Email Address</FormLabel>
                <Input
                  type="email"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="Email"
                  ref={register}
                />
                <FormErrorMessage>{errors?.email?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
                <FormHelperText>
                  We are obviously giving this straight to Facebook.
                </FormHelperText>
              </FormControl>
            </HStack>
            <HStack spacing="50px" mb="15px">
              <FormControl
                isInvalid={!!errors?.subject?.message}
                errortext={errors?.subject?.message}
                p="4"
                isRequired
              >
                <FormLabel>Subject</FormLabel>
                <Input
                  type="text"
                  name="subject"
                  placeholder="Subject"
                  ref={register}
                />
                <FormErrorMessage>{errors?.subject?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
                <FormHelperText>
                  We are obviously giving this straight to Facebook.
                </FormHelperText>
              </FormControl>
              <FormControl
                isInvalid={!!errors?.enquiry?.message}
                errortext={errors?.enquiry?.message}
                p="4"
                isRequired
              >
                <FormLabel>ENQUIRY TYPE</FormLabel>
                <InputGroup borderColor="#E0E1E7">
                  <Select placeholder="Advertising" type="text" name="name">
                    <option value="option1">Option 1</option>
                    <option value="option2">Option 2</option>
                    <option value="option3">Option 3</option>
                  </Select>
                </InputGroup>
                <FormErrorMessage>{errors?.enquiry?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
              </FormControl>
            </HStack>
            <FormControl
              isInvalid={!!errors?.textarea?.message}
              errortext={errors?.textarea?.message}
              p="4"
              isRequired
            >
              <FormLabel>MESSAGES</FormLabel>
              <Textarea placeholder="enter your messages" />
              <FormErrorMessage>{errors?.textarea?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
            </FormControl>
            <Button
              onClick={handleSubmit(onSubmit)}
              p="4"
              mx="4"
              mt="6"
              w="90%"
              colorScheme="blue"
              variant="solid"
              // disabled={!!errors.email || !!errors.password}
            >
              Login
            </Button>
          </form>
        </Box>
      </Flex>
    </Container>
  );
}
